main event: A civilian reported seeing a bright, powerful object moving swiftly at treetop level in Lewisburg, Ohio on May 18, 1965.
interesting points: The object started moving downward suddenly, then continued moving swiftly.
As the object came closer, it seemed quite brightly lit.
The object disappeared suddenly, but was then seen again hovering over a field across the road before disappearing again over the treetops.
During the entire observation, a running noise was heard.
The witness's sister and brother-in-law also saw the object.
witnesses: civilian, including the witness's sister and brother-in-law
